__TOC__

The following are two tables of packages in main that do not have '''any''' bug subscribers.  Subsequently, it is likely that no one is watching them for new bug reports or reviewing the reported bugs.  I've divided the list of packages into two tables - one of packages that are likely sync'ed with Debian and one that contains packages that have Ubuntu changes or are Ubuntu specific.  The tables are sorted by the quantity of open bug reports.  Language packs were also excluded but attached you'll also find the  <nowiki>[[ attachment:unsubscribed-packages.txt | original csv file ]]</nowiki>.  The list was generated on 2009-08-31.
